		"description":{
			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>Though these ornate chamois gloves fit snugly, your fingertips always seem just short of touching something within them.</i></p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Hands Slot</b><b>:</b> Uncommon</p>\n<p class=\"subheading\"><b>Power (Minor Action)</b></p><p>You touch an unattended item to store it in one of the gloves. Each glove can hold one item, and each item must weigh no more than 10 pounds. Items have no weight while within the gloves.</p><p class=\"subheading\"><b>Power (Minor Action)</b></p><p>You cause an item stored within one glove to materialize in your hand. Weapons so produced are ready to wield, but items that require an additional action to equip (such as shields) must still be readied.</p>",
